Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:26.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(978.8,252.706)}下       回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:26.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp20\pos(972.4,524.353)}翼貓 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  最終回  翼貓  其五
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說  是真的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加可怕了
